  03 Jul 2006; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> xvattr-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc; bug #139010.

  07 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  xvattr-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  Changed the dirty hack to disable GTK to a proper patch to xvattr so that it
  has a --without-gtk switch. Port to modular X.

